original_title: Keeping the Promise: AHF 30 Years Documentary
overview: Through interviews with key AIDS Healthcare Foundation (AHF) stakeholders from over the years coupled with archival video footage culled from AHF's 30 years of advocacy, care and activism, 'Keeping the Promise' tells a compelling story of AHF's history while offering a glimpse of, and road map to its future.
title: Keeping the Promise: AHF 30 Years Documentary
